      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=gh12ctcr6x]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=gh12ctcr6x]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=pnq9hno50d]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=pnq9hno50d]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=gxaw04hwgp]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=gxaw04hwgp]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=fv24snun5b]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=fv24snun5b]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=v7nvdu0nzm]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=v7nvdu0nzm]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=xej0tj1e5b]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=xej0tj1e5b]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=vjz1fy80tj]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=vjz1fy80tj]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=otf0okozrk]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=otf0okozrk]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=jo8llgh0x6]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=jo8llgh0x6]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ago8ctfnca]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ago8ctfnca]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"ProceduralEdgeBreak_6.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163195/ProceduralEdgeBreak_6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725613317&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=320\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163195/ProceduralEdgeBreak_6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725613317&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"714\" data-width=\"1695\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"635863075\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"ProceduralEdgeBreak_6.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163195\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"27\" data-media-id=\"5347952b-5185-4829-b2d3-ca41dc69507d\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163195/ProceduralEdgeBreak_6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725613317&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=640 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163195/ProceduralEdgeBreak_6.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1761725613317&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=320 1x\" /></span><p>At Pixar, we frequently utilize procedural material networks for shading.  It has many benefits, including being able to re-position the asset at different camera depths without having to worry about the texture resolution.  Procedural shading also allows for easy and dynamic breakup variation across multiple instances.</p><p>These lessons will walk you through the basics of procedural shaders, through to some practical everyday examples that you can apply to your shading networks and props.</p><h1 id=\"Procedural-StartHere\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"fv24snun5b\">Start Here</span></strong></h1><hr /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/623607817/Patterns+Noises\" data-linked-resource-id=\"623607817\" data-linked-resource-version=\"8\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"patterns_thumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163195/patterns_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760091338735&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163195/patterns_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760091338735&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"400\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"623542449\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"patterns_thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163195\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"27\" data-media-id=\"b6425c8a-8769-49a0-9d1c-a0f681e5fee5\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163195/patterns_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760091338735&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163195/patterns_thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760091338735&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ago8ctfnca\">Patterns &amp; Noises</span></strong><br />A guide to RenderMan&rsquo;s pattern nodes </p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a href=\"/wiki/spaces/RU/pages/623509593/PxrDirt+PxrCurvature\" data-linked-resource-id=\"623509593\" data-linked-resource-version=\"7\" data-linked-resource-type=\"page\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"PxrCurvature_Thumb.jpg\" width=\"261\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163195/PxrCurvature_Thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760090899743&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/599163195/PxrCurvature_Thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760090899743&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"400\" data-width=\"400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"623607863\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"PxrCurvature_Thumb.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"599163195\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"27\" data-media-id=\"7092beb5-c251-4296-91cb-0fcb5378fe8e\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163195/PxrCurvature_Thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760090899743&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/599163195/PxrCurvature_Thumb.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1760090899743&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=261&amp;height=261 1x\" /></span></a><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"xej0tj1e5b\">PxrDirt &amp; PxrCurvature</span></strong><br />Learn the basics of the PxrDirt &amp; PxrCurvature.</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"Procedural-NextSteps\"><strong><span data-colorid=\"otf0okozrk\">Next Steps</span></strong></h1></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout three-equal\" data-layout=\"three-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a hre